Minimalistic style: A pristine white workspace viewed from above, featuring a sleek ceramic funnel filtering colorful geometric shapes - cubes, spheres, and pyramids in vibrant blues, oranges, and greens. The shapes pour in chaotically from above, but only matching outline slots below the funnel accept specific forms, while mismatched pieces scatter and fade into shadow. Clean parallel lines suggest data flow, with subtle grid patterns etched into the surface. The composition emphasizes order emerging from chaos, with sharp shadows creating depth against the stark white background. Soft directional lighting from the upper left corner.
